The paper focuses on building an automated testing system for deep learning systems, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of differential behavior criteria to generate corner cases for testing also relates to software engineering (cs.SE) and system testing (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper explores the use of photo-realistic images and Generative Adversarial Networks (GAN) for testing, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV).
